            "id": "s_l1_1",
            "type": "text",
            "title": "Python the Calculator 🧮",
            "content": "# Math Made Easy\n\nPython is an incredibly powerful calculator! You can perform all kinds of math operations.\n\nIn this lesson, you'll master:\n\n* ➕ Addition, subtraction\n* ✖️ Multiplication, division\n* 🔢 Floor division, modulo\n* 📈 Exponentiation"
        },
        {
            "id": "s_l1_2",
            "type": "text",
            "title": "The Big 7 Operators ➕➖✖️➗",
            "content": "# Arithmetic Operators Table\n\n| Operator | Name | Example | Result |\n|----------|------|---------|--------|\n| `+` | Addition | `5 + 3` | `8` |\n| `-` | Subtraction | `5 - 3` | `2` |\n| `*` | Multiplication | `5 * 3` | `15` |\n| `/` | Division | `5 / 2` | `2.5` |\n| `//` | Floor Division | `5 // 2` | `2` |\n| `%` | Modulo | `5 % 2` | `1` |\n| `**` | Exponent | `5 ** 2` | `25` |"
        },
        {
            "id": "s_l1_3",
            "type": "code",
            "title": "Basic Operations 💻",
            "content": "Try out the four basic operations:",
            "codeSnippet": "a = 15\nb = 4\n\nprint(\"Addition:\", a + b)        # 19\nprint(\"Subtraction:\", a - b)     # 11\nprint(\"Multiplication:\", a * b)  # 60\nprint(\"Division:\", a / b)        # 3.75",
            "codeLanguage": "python",
            "canRunCode": true
        },
