            "id": "s_l1_5",
            "type": "text",
            "title": "Division Deep Dive ➗",
            "content": "# Two Types of Division\n\n**True Division `/`**\n* Always returns a float\n* `10 / 4` → `2.5`\n* `10 / 2` → `5.0` (still float!)\n\n**Floor Division `//`**\n* Rounds DOWN to integer\n* `10 // 4` → `2`\n* `10 // 2` → `5`"
        },
        {
            "id": "s_l1_6",
            "type": "code",
            "title": "Division Comparison 💻",
            "content": "See the difference between / and //:",
            "codeSnippet": "print(\"True division:\")\nprint(\"17 / 5 =\", 17 / 5)    # 3.4\nprint(\"17 / 1 =\", 17 / 1)    # 17.0\n\nprint(\"\\nFloor division:\")\nprint(\"17 // 5 =\", 17 // 5)  # 3\nprint(\"17 // 1 =\", 17 // 1)  # 17",
            "codeLanguage": "python",
            "canRunCode": true
        },
        {
