            "id": "s_l1_14",
            "type": "text",
            "title": "Negative Numbers ➖",
            "content": "# Working with Negatives\n\nAll operators work with negative numbers:\n\n* `-5 + 3` → `-2`\n* `-5 * -3` → `15` (negative × negative = positive)\n* `10 / -2` → `-5.0`\n* `-10 // 3` → `-4` (rounds toward negative infinity)"
        },
        {
            "id": "s_l1_15",
            "type": "code",
            "title": "Negative Number Math 💻",
            "content": "Operations with negative numbers:",
            "codeSnippet": "print(\"-5 + 3 =\", -5 + 3)\nprint(\"-5 * -3 =\", -5 * -3)\nprint(\"10 / -2 =\", 10 / -2)\n\n# Floor division with negatives\nprint(\"-10 // 3 =\", -10 // 3)  # -4 (toward negative infinity)\nprint(\"10 // -3 =\", 10 // -3)  # -4",
            "codeLanguage": "python",
            "canRunCode": true
        },
