            "title": "Working with Floats 🔢",
            "content": "# Floating-Point Arithmetic\n\nOperations with floats work as expected:\n\n* `3.5 + 2.1` → `5.6`\n* `4.0 * 2.5` → `10.0`\n\n**But beware of precision issues:**\n* `0.1 + 0.2` → `0.30000000000000004`\n\nThis is a computer limitation, not a Python bug!"
        },
