            "title": "Pro Tip 🚀",
            "content": "## Handling Float Precision\n\nFor money and precision-critical calculations:\n\n```python\n# Use round() for display\nresult = 0.1 + 0.2\nprint(round(result, 2))  # 0.3\n\n# Or use Decimal module\nfrom decimal import Decimal\nprint(Decimal('0.1') + Decimal('0.2'))\n```"
        },
